
# Creative Chat

Creative Chat is a simple web application that allows users to post anonymous messages and view messages posted by others. It provides a platform for anonymous communication, enabling users to express themselves freely without revealing their identities.

## Features

- **Secure conversation**: All your messages will be secured in google sheets (we know google for documents secrecy) where you can delete or save whenever.
- **Real-Time Updates**: Messages are displayed in real-time without the need to refresh the page.
- **Responsive Design**: The website is designed to work seamlessly on desktop and mobile devices.
- **Simple Interface**: Easy-to-use interface for submitting and viewing messages.
- **Custom theme**: The website features the css code organized so you can change it to your liking.

## Technologies Used

- **HTML**: Markup language for structuring the website content.
- **CSS**: Stylesheet language for styling the website layout and design.
- **JavaScript**: Programming language for client-side functionality and interactions.
- **Google Sheets API**: Used for storing and retrieving message data.
- **SweetAlert2**: JavaScript library for displaying Customizable alert messages.
- **Github**: Used as Platform-as-a-Service (PaaS) used for deploying and hosting the website.

